        <abstract>
            <p>Remarks on Darwinism’s reception. The radical press shies away, out of ignorance, because CD may be made out to be a Tory. He has met a Darwinian Marchioness.</p>
            <p>The mystery of sex is the origin of all religion.</p>
        </abstract>
